info.description:
# Introduction

This API allows you to perform CRUD for users and their respective profiles.

# Schema

**User**

``` json
{
    "id": "string",
    "username": "string",
    "first_name": "string",
    "last_name": "string",
    "verified": boolean,
    "create_date": "date",
    "update_date": "date"
}

```

**Profile**

``` json
{
    "id": "string",
    "userId": "string",
    "picture_url": "string",
    "persona": {
        "preferred_name": "string",
        "suffix": "string",
        "prefix": "string",
        "dob": "string",
        "sex": "string",
        "languages": [
            "string"
        ],
        "race": "string",
        "ethnicity": "string",
        "nationality": "string",
        "pronouns": [
            "string"
        ]
    },
    "work": {
        "jobs": [
            {
                "company": "string",
                "occupation": "string",
                "location": {
                    "city": "string",
                    "state": "string",
                    "country": "string",
                    "zip": "string"
                }
            }
        ],
        "looking": "boolean"
    },
    "addresses": [
        {
            "street": "string",
            "city": "string",
            "state": "string",
            "zip": "string",
            "country": "string",
            "primary": "boolean"
        }
    ],
    "social": {
        "personal": {
            "facebook": "string",
            "instagram": "string",
            "portfolio": "string",
            "tiktok": "string",
            "twitter": "string"
        },
        "professional": {
            "github": "string",
            "linked_in": "string"
        },
        "gaming": {
            "nintendo": "string",
            "origin": "string",
            "playstation": "string",
            "riot": "string",
            "steam": "string",
            "xbox": "string"
        }
    },
    "create_date": "date",
    "update_date": "date"
}

```

**Error**

``` json
{
    "message": "string",
    "name": "string"
}

```

**Validation Errors**

``` json
{
    "validation_errors": [
        {
            "value": "string",
            "msg": "string",
            "param": "string",
            "location": "string"
        }
    ]
}

```

